Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.98,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:16.01,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:20.18,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:28.35,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:34.86,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:39.78,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:46.91,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:51.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.55,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:58.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:06.14,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:09.77,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:16.94,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:28.06,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Challenge From the Past:\N The Horrifying Zera"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:37.97,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.68,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you look nice as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.45,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:45.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.31,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi! Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0} is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.03,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay! I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.02,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That doesn't look half bad, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.62,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You think so?\N It isn't too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.95,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, I was thinking\N it's not flashy {\b0}enough{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should try wearing a bracelet or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:12.33,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that wouldn't suit me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.98,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go. Anzu is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.87,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show her your cool side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.17,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you {\i1}talking{\i0} about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.44,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just talking to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.95,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:28.88,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you stick by me, I'll make Anzu fall for you in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.64,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Stop picking on me, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:39.87,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.38,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:42.97,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:49.84,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really important to my other Self, so I want to make sure I don't damage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.71,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi and the Other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the outer and inner \Nsides of Yugi's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:02.11,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met the Other Yugi in Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:08.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't tell you guys, but the me that Duels isn't the usual me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:14.99,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm always resting in my heart.\N I change to my Other Self to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:21.42,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His other heart is inside the Millennium Puzzle... So says Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.61,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.93,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.\N Let's hurry to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:28.42,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that kid okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.09,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:39.32,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been talking to himself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.82,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's going through a lot.\N He's at that age, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.60,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was that way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.58,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.68,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yugi. Do you have some free time this Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have anything to do, so if you have some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.73,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,want to go do something somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.79,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.38,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.29,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting my fortune told!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.96,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geez... That's so childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.58,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have something quite magnificent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.90,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.73,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.40,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this! It's very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.40,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.53,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.82,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've studied countless rare treasures from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.73,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I may just be able to determine what I'm looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.83,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's really just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.63,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.01,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen any quite like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.13,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.58,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, go to school before me!\N I'm going after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.33,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he leading me somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.06,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.47,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.86,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.15,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's puzzle was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.52,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.14,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.99,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try looking for Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.11,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.60,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stolen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.61,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the {\i1}hell{\i0} is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.97,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.85,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Ring senses a bad omen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Items contain memories of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:32.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou must be the one to hold the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Any person who makes themselves {\i1}his{\i0} enemy becomes {\i1}mine{\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.81,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.32,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.45,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.42,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to give it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.73,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.58,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to give it back, defeat me in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.86,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.69,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making me Duel you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.83,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for me to answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have but two\N options to choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept the Duel? Or will you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Yugi Mutou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:27.71,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who defeated Pegasus and became the winner of Duelist Kingdom doesn't look like much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:33.96,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the power of the Millennium Puzzle and the other Yugi that defeated him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:37.37,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly is residing within the Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.39,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the identity of the other Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is my objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really is who I think he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.98,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to Duel you?\N Can't you just return my Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.21,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.25,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you better keep your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:56.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me... can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.44,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.66,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.03,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still able to call to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.76,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to fight this Duel alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.18,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.18,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sense something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:20.01,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone is trying to see my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.49,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you can't lend me your power like usual, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:24.91,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.97,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll fight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.03,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll surely get back the Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.84,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm counting on you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.21,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. You're ready to Duel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.68,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it's your turn first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.81,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I play Elf Warrior in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.40,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.92,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a monster in defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.31,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.28,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've heard that voice somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.82,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is it?\N It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Warrior, attack the Defense Mode Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:11:00.24,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,When Cyber Pod is attacked while in face-down Defense Position,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.77,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyber Pod's Effect activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:10.90,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is flipped from reverse, all Monsters on the field are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:16.25,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And both players are to draw five new cards from the top of their decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:22.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,We then both Summon any Level Four or lower Monster Cards we've drawn to the field in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.87,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Fang in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.10,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mecha Hunter and\N Ground Attacker Bugroth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.67,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Cyber Pod he played earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he playing a Machine Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.38,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be Bandit Keith?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.14,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Keith!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:51.42,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really seems like a different person, but there's no mistaking that bandana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:57.19,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was defeated by Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} in Duelist Kingdom and then ejected from the island by Pegasus for using dirty tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.08,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.64,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that this man is known as "Bandit Keith".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.94,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"This man"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.54,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,After the fact, Keith was thrown into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.61,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.73,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does he call himself "this man" as if he's talking about another person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.58,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why is he after me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.23,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising that he has a grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.04,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Had you guys not been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith would have gotten his hands on a large cash prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:58.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as earning back the title of "Number One U.S. Champion Duelist".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.65,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.25,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Machine King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.79,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:19.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,By Machine King's Effect, its Attack goes up by 100 points for every Machine-type Monster on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Silver Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.74,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Punch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:31.79,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.91,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.07,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.61,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems you're quite scared of my Machine Monster Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:47.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play an Ultra Rare Card and scare you even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.27,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Megasonic Eye in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:55.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And by Machine King's Effect, its Attack goes up by 100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Machine King, attack his Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.52,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, your Monsters are being annihilated one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:16.34,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you call out your other like you did back in the Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keith shouldn't know about my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.85,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.12,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that Keith?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yugi's Millennium Puzzle was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:33.10,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be some guy after the title Yugi earned in Duelist Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:36.45,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be after Yugi. Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.02,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.89,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Where are you headed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.40,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't class already started already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.05,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mutou's really sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.81,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so painful, all he could do was call our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.78,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry up and go, Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go visit him, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.21,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.63,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Mutou-{\i1}kun{\i0} back with you safe and sound~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.25,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.63,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he finds out, we're in trouble later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.68,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars smell worse than piss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.97,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just {\i1}wrong{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.42,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about "shi-"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.31,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:22.93,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach out to the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.29,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and call out the other soul within.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.63,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let things go your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.23,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.98,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon, in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.69,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dark Knight Gaia as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:48.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I polymerize Curse of Dragon with Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.66,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now his Attack Power will be greater than Machine King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.64,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia, attack Mecha Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Dragon Lance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.05,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Machine King's Attack goes down by 100 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.53,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Mode Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.86,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mega Sonic Eye and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.39,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ground Attacker Bugroth will be switched in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.50,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,And I play the rare card known as Machine Conversion Factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.52,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,which increases the Attack and Defense Points of all Machine-type Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.16,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,...by 300 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.11,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.53,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, Gaia the Dragon Knight is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.08,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Machine King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.37,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Dragon Knight Gaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:48.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you gonna just sit and watch while you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to keep the title you earned from Duelist Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.37,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it have been {\i1}another{\i0} man that defeated Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.52,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious! Like you {\i1}usually{\i0} are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.17,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it were the other me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.56,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he wouldn't give up even when driven into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.71,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He would calmly analyze the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:09.99,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Machine Army has to have a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.02,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.51,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon's Summon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.38,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even machines have a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.27,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what that is right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.90,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Makiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this acid rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.87,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I play Demon's Summon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:53.52,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,While weakening your Machines, the rain {\i1}increases{\i0} Demon's Summon's electrical attack power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.37,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.68,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.03,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,A turn around!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.33,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.60,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,He is much better than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:14.06,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been holding back so far in order to see the other soul within the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time I dropped the act and got serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.74,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use our special\N replica cards to attack him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.46,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and force out the other soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.33,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,From here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.08,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could these be arrows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi went this way, right Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.86,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,But who would...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.02,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.49,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.72,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go. It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.17,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card Angel's Charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:55.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw three cards from my deck, then discard two after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.98,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Rare Card! Ritual of Zera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ritual of Zera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:30.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a card that lets you initiate the advent of Zera once you sacrifice Monsters equaling 8 stars or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.95,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.19,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Zera is the strongest Monster of the Demon-Fiend Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.57,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.07,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only three original cards in the entire world...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.78,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even {\i1}seen{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.24,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an ultra rare card even among other Ultra Rares.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa told me himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:54.95,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I Tribute Ground Attacker Bugroth and Megasonic Eye in order to Summon Zera!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.63,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon's Summon can't win against Zera!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Claw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.05,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an Ultra Rare Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.20,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.56,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no ordinary Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Power of Darkness is present throughout the entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.30,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.61,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:51.77,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.95,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's the matter? Just reach out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.54,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach out to your other self in the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.21,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know that man's true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.28,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.96,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? There's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.45,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that invincible Yugi from Duelist Kingdom run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:22.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My other self... At this rate, I can't get the Millennium Puzzle back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:26.01,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Come on out, other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.22,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.47,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:39.36,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prove Yugi's true identity, Keith appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:44.85,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he does, Keith overwhelms Yugi with his rare cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.06,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't he acting a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:48.89,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.28,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's Millennium Puzzle has been smashed apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.54,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi hurries to put together the Puzzle in a raging fire...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.00,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.75,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Broken Millennium Puzzle"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.39,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:26.66,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:36.23,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:47.41,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:55.48,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.80,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:06.01,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:11.19,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:16.26,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:21.43,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.78,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:29.18,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:35.55,Subtitle,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, always...
